data.description: Welcome home! This charming full brick home is in a great neighborhood close Sooner Park and Adams Golf Course. New carpet & paint & some ceiling fans in 2023. Vinyl windows. Kitchen is light and bright and open to the den with cozy gas log fireplace & built in bookshelves. Formal living area plus large dining area and lots of natural light. Primary bedroom with full bath & direct access to the laundry room. Newer water heater. Garage entry is level and on the back of the home with workshop space. Offering a private entrance and nice patio entertaining space in the back. Perfect for entertaining, planting a garden or parking a boat or RV. All appliances including washer & dryer will remain!
